# Ollama Modelfile for the fine-tuned HORUS-OSINT model.
# Usage (on the GPU box, after copying your GGUF into the Ollama container/host):
#   ollama create horus-osint -f Modelfile
#
# Then HORUS_MODEL_NAME=horus-osint (the default) picks it up.

FROM ./Horus-OSINT.gguf

# Match the fine-tuning chat template / stop tokens for Llama-3.
PARAMETER temperature 0.2
PARAMETER top_p 0.9
PARAMETER stop "<|eot_id|>"
PARAMETER stop "<|end_of_text|>"

# The model already produces a sectioned Intelligence Report Card; the provider prompts it
# for EXECUTIVE SUMMARY / GEOPOLITICAL CONTEXT / THREAT ASSESSMENT / CONCLUSION.
SYSTEM """You are HORUS, a defensive OSINT intelligence analyst. You reason over correlated,
retrieved facts and produce concise, sectioned intelligence report cards. You never invent
entities or figures; you synthesize and explain what the evidence shows."""
